Continuous health checks for route availability
Used by: Monitoring systems, development teams
Frequency: Every 30 seconds for active routes
âš¡ API Performance Characteristics
Response Times
â”œâ”€â”€ Registration APIs: < 500ms (database writes)
â”œâ”€â”€ Configuration APIs: < 200ms (cached reads)
â”œâ”€â”€ Testing APIs: < 2s (includes external calls)
â”œâ”€â”€ Analytics APIs: < 1s (aggregated data)
â””â”€â”€ Core Notification API: < 200ms (production optimized)
Rate Limits
â”œâ”€â”€ Registration APIs: 10 requests/hour per team
â”œâ”€â”€ Testing APIs: 100 requests/hour during onboarding
â”œâ”€â”€ Management APIs: 1000 requests/hour per team
â””â”€â”€ Production APIs: Per route configuration (100-10000/minute)
Availability SLAs
â”œâ”€â”€ Onboarding APIs: 99.5% uptime
â”œâ”€â”€ Testing APIs: 99.0% uptime (lower priority)
â”œâ”€â”€ Production APIs: 99.9% uptime
â””â”€â”€ Analytics APIs: 99.5% uptime
