ğŸ’° Better Business ROI: Focus on capabilities with clear business outcomes
ğŸš€ Innovation Pipeline: Systematic identification of new opportunities
ğŸ¯ Platform Differentiation: Solve jobs better than competing solutions
Bottom Line: JTBD framework transforms notification platform from feature-driven to outcome-driven, ensuring every capability delivers real user and business value while providing clear innovation direction.

