â”œâ”€â”€ Business outcome correlation analysis
â””â”€â”€ Strategic platform evolution planning

ANNUALLY: Job Strategy Review
â”œâ”€â”€ Market and organizational change assessment
â”œâ”€â”€ Job prioritization review and updates
â”œâ”€â”€ Platform capability roadmap revision
â”œâ”€â”€ Competitive job performance analysis
â””â”€â”€ Investment allocation optimization
Optimization Decision Framework
PERFORMANCE ISSUE IDENTIFICATION:
â”œâ”€â”€ Job success rate below target (e.g., <85% satisfaction)
â”œâ”€â”€ Business outcome correlation weakening
â”œâ”€â”€ User behavior patterns changing
â”œâ”€â”€ Competitive solutions emerging
â””â”€â”€ New job needs appearing

OPTIMIZATION PRIORITY MATRIX:
HIGH IMPACT + QUICK FIX:
â”œâ”€â”€ Content optimization (tone, information, timing)
â”œâ”€â”€ User interface improvements (buttons, layout)
â”œâ”€â”€ Message personalization enhancements
â””â”€â”€ Workflow streamlining

HIGH IMPACT + COMPLEX FIX:
â”œâ”€â”€ New capability development
â”œâ”€â”€ Platform integration improvements
â”œâ”€â”€ Advanced personalization systems
â””â”€â”€ Predictive job support features

LOW IMPACT + QUICK FIX:
â”œâ”€â”€ Visual design improvements
â”œâ”€â”€ Technical performance optimization
â”œâ”€â”€ Error message clarity
â””â”€â”€ Help documentation updates
Step 2: Innovation Pipeline Management
New Job Identification Process
UNDERSERVED JOB DISCOVERY:
â”œâ”€â”€ User interview insights: "What jobs aren't being solved well?"
â”œâ”€â”€ Behavioral analytics: "Where do users struggle or abandon tasks?"
â”œâ”€â”€ Support ticket analysis: "What problems occur repeatedly?"
â”œâ”€â”€ Competitive analysis: "What jobs do competitors solve better?"
â””â”€â”€ Organizational change impact: "What new jobs are emerging?"

JOB OPPORTUNITY ASSESSMENT:
â”œâ”€â”€ User pain severity: How much does failure hurt?
â”œâ”€â”€ Frequency of need: How often does this job occur?
â”œâ”€â”€ Current solution gaps: How poorly is this job served now?
â”œâ”€â”€ Platform fit: Can notifications meaningfully help?
â”œâ”€â”€ Business value potential: What outcomes would improvement drive?
â””â”€â”€ Technical feasibility: Can we build an effective solution?

INNOVATION PRIORITIZATION:
â”œâ”€â”€ Critical underserved jobs: Immediate development priority
â”œâ”€â”€ Growth opportunity jobs: Medium-term development focus
â”œâ”€â”€ Emerging need jobs: Research and experimentation phase
â”œâ”€â”€ Niche high-value jobs: Specialized solution consideration
â””â”€â”€ Future potential jobs: Long-term roadmap inclusion
Capability Evolution Strategy
