NEW CAPABILITY DEVELOPMENT:
â”œâ”€â”€ Job-first design: Start with job definition, not technical capability
â”œâ”€â”€ Multi-platform job optimization: Design for job success across all channels
â”œâ”€â”€ Success metric definition: Establish clear job outcome measurements
â”œâ”€â”€ User validation: Test job solution effectiveness before full development
â””â”€â”€ Integration planning: Ensure new capabilities enhance overall job ecosystem
