## ğŸ“ **Learning and Getting Started**

### **Q18: I'm a developer who needs to integrate with this platform. Where do I start?**

**ANSWER:** "We have a step-by-step onboarding process with lots of help - like driver's education for the platform"
DEVELOPER ONBOARDING JOURNEY:

WEEK 1: LEARN THE BASICS
â”œâ”€â”€ Read platform overview documentation
â”œâ”€â”€ Understand namespaces, schemas, and capabilities
â”œâ”€â”€ Review example integrations from other teams
â”œâ”€â”€ Join developer Slack channel for questions
â””â”€â”€ Schedule intro meeting with platform team

WEEK 2: PLAN YOUR INTEGRATION
â”œâ”€â”€ Identify your notification needs (what capabilities?) â”œâ”€â”€ Choose your target platforms (mobile, desktop, email?) â”œâ”€â”€ Design your user experience (what should users see?) â”œâ”€â”€ Estimate your notification volume (how many per day?) â””â”€â”€ Submit integration request form

WEEK 3: GET APPROVED AND SET UP
â”œâ”€â”€ Platform team reviews your request (2-3 days)
â”œâ”€â”€ Receive your API credentials and documentation
â”œâ”€â”€ Access to testing environment and tools
